<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="da">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>August fylder 15 – MAX BRAINROT EDITION</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bangers&family=Luckiest+Guy&family=Comic+Neue:wght@700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');

  *{box-sizing:border-box;}

  html,body{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    background:#050208;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    min-height:100vh;
    font-family:'Comic Neue', sans-serif;
  }

  .card{
    position:relative;
    width:920px;
    height:600px;
    border-radius:20px;
    overflow:hidden;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 10% 8%, #FF2E92 0%, transparent 32%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 92% 12%, #00E5FF 0%, transparent 30%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 85% 92%, #FFD400 0%, transparent 34%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 8% 90%, #7C4DFF 0%, transparent 34%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, #FF5C00 0%, transparent 40%),
      #1a0f22;
    box-shadow:0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    border:8px solid #fff;
    outline:4px dashed #FFD400;
    outline-offset:-16px;
  }

  .sticker{
    position:absolute;
    z-index:5;
    filter:drop-shadow(0 3px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5));
  }
  .s1{ top:10px; left:14px; font-size:34px; transform:rotate(-18deg);}
  .s2{ top:8px; left:230px; font-size:26px; transform:rotate(12deg);}
  .s3{ top:14px; right:230px; font-size:30px; transform:rotate(-8deg);}
  .s4{ top:20px; right:16px; font-size:32px; transform:rotate(16deg);}
  .s5{ bottom:130px; left:8px; font-size:28px; transform:rotate(10deg);}
  .s6{ bottom:14px; left:230px; font-size:24px; transform:rotate(-10deg);}
  .s7{ bottom:130px; right:8px; font-size:30px; transform:rotate(-14deg);}
  .s8{ bottom:14px; right:250px; font-size:26px; transform:rotate(8deg);}
  .s9{ top:46%; left:2px; font-size:22px; transform:rotate(-90deg);}
  .s10{ top:46%; right:2px; font-size:22px; transform:rotate(90deg);}

  .marquee{
    position:absolute;
    top:0; left:0; right:0;
    background:#000;
    color:#FFD400;
    font-family:'Bangers', cursive;
    font-size:15px;
    letter-spacing:2px;
    padding:5px 0;
    white-space:nowrap;
    overflow:hidden;
    z-index:6;
    border-bottom:3px solid #FFD400;
  }
  .marquee span{
    display:inline-block;
    padding-left:100%;
    animation:scroll 14s linear infinite;
  }
  @keyframes scroll{
    0%{ transform:translateX(0); }
    100%{ transform:translateX(-100%); }
  }

  .content{
    position:relative;
    z-index:2;
    display:flex;
    height:100%;
    padding-top:30px;
  }

  .avatar-col{
    width:260px;
    flex-shrink:0;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    padding:16px;
    border-right:4px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    position:relative;
  }

  .avatar{
    width:150px;
    height:150px;
    margin-bottom:6px;
    filter:drop-shadow(0 6px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.4));
    transform:rotate(-3deg);
  }

  .toilet{
    width:60px;
    position:absolute;
    top:18px;
    right:14px;
    transform:rotate(12deg);
    filter:drop-shadow(0 3px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.4));
  }

  .lvl-badge{
    font-family:'Luckiest Guy', cursive;
    font-size:24px;
    color:#FFD400;
    -webkit-text-stroke:2px #000;
    text-shadow:3px 3px 0 #FF2E92, 6px 6px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    letter-spacing:1px;
    text-align:center;
    line-height:1.1;
  }

  .sigma-tag{
    margin-top:8px;
    background:#000;
    color:#00E5FF;
    font-size:10.5px;
    letter-spacing:1px;
    padding:5px 9px;
    border-radius:20px;
    font-weight:700;
    border:2px solid #00E5FF;
    text-transform:uppercase;
    transform:rotate(-4deg);
  }
  .ohio-tag{
    margin-top:8px;
    background:#FF5C00;
    color:#000;
    font-size:10.5px;
    letter-spacing:0.5px;
    padding:5px 9px;
    border-radius:20px;
    font-weight:700;
    border:2px solid #000;
    transform:rotate(3deg);
  }

  .panel{
    flex:1;
    padding:18px 36px 22px;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    justify-content:space-between;
  }

  .top{ display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:4px; }

  .eyebrow{
    font-size:12.5px;
    letter-spacing:1px;
    color:#fff;
    background:#FF2E92;
    display:inline-block;
    padding:4px 11px;
    border-radius:6px;
    font-weight:700;
    transform:rotate(-2deg);
    width:fit-content;
    border:2px solid #000;
    font-family:'Comic Neue', sans-serif;
  }

  h1{
    margin:6px 0 0;
    font-family:'Bangers', cursive;
    font-size:50px;
    line-height:0.92;
    color:#FFD400;
    -webkit-text-stroke:2.5px #000;
    text-shadow:4px 4px 0 #7C4DFF, 8px 8px 0 #FF5C00, 12px 12px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    letter-spacing:1px;
  }

  .subrizz{
    font-family:'Luckiest Guy', cursive;
    font-size:15px;
    color:#00E5FF;
    -webkit-text-stroke:1px #000;
    margin-top:4px;
    transform:rotate(-1deg);
  }

  .quest{
    background:#fff;
    border:4px solid #000;
    border-radius:14px;
    padding:14px 18px;
    margin-top:10px;
    box-shadow:7px 7px 0 #000;
    transform:rotate(0.5deg);
  }
  .quest-title{
    font-family:'Bangers', cursive;
    font-size:18px;
    color:#FF2E92;
    letter-spacing:0.5px;
    margin-bottom:5px;
  }
  .quest-body{
    font-size:14.5px;
    line-height:1.45;
    color:#111;
    margin:0;
    font-weight:700;
  }
  .quest-body b{
    background:#FFD400;
    padding:0 4px;
    border-radius:3px;
  }
  .quest-body .cyan{ background:#00E5FF; padding:0 4px; border-radius:3px; }

  .footer{
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:space-between;
    margin-top:10px;
  }
  .from{
    font-family:'Luckiest Guy', cursive;
    font-size:17px;
    color:#fff;
    -webkit-text-stroke:1px #000;
    transform:rotate(-1.5deg);
  }

  .stamp{
    font-family:'Bangers', cursive;
    font-size:15px;
    color:#111;
    background:#00E5FF;
    border:3px solid #000;
    border-radius:8px;
    padding:7px 11px;
    transform:rotate(7deg);
    letter-spacing:0.5px;
    box-shadow:4px 4px 0 #000;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">

  <div class="marquee"><span>🚨 GYAT ALERT 🚨 ‼️ RIZZLER LEVEL 15 UNLOCKED ‼️ ONLY IN OHIO 🌽 NPC MODE: OFF 🗿 FANUM TAX INCOMING 💀 SIGMA GRINDSET ACTIVATED 🔥 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 🚨 GYAT ALERT 🚨 ‼️ RIZZLER LEVEL 15 UNLOCKED ‼️ ONLY IN OHIO 🌽 NPC MODE: OFF 🗿 FANUM TAX INCOMING 💀 SIGMA GRINDSET ACTIVATED 🔥</span></div>

  <div class="sticker s1">💀</div>
